            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ". Joab fleeing to the horns of the altar is slain there, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bldvs",
            "text": " 1 Kings 2:28-34",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ". Benaiah is put in Joab’s room, and Zadok in Abiathar’s, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bldvs",
            "text": " 1 Kings 2:35",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ". Shimei confined to Jerusalem; going thence to Gath is put to death, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bldvs",
            "text": " 1 Kings 2:36-46",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ". ",
